{
  "stem": "3040.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "During the night, if you wanted-- you had to get up, to get out to the latrine, the latrine was full of dead people-- stacked up.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Naked-- naked corpses, stacked up like wood, one on top of the other, because people were dying during the night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were pulling them out, undress them, put them-- stacked them up, because, you know, after a couple of hours, the body gets stiff.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were stacking up just like wood, this way and this way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So when you got in during the night, [INAUDIBLE] you'll-- you will find all these corpses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every night.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every-- every day.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the morning, we had to carry these corpses out to the field.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they burned them, because they didn't--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to do that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't have crematoriums there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They burned bodies in the open field.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So after the night, there was always a lot of people, a lot of dead people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We carried them out, and they put them to fire.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They burned them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was always smoke going and smoldering, always.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Day and night.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't-- I didn't-- I don't recall knowing anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somehow you become so isolated inward that you-- it's very seldom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There are people who made and carried over some friendships, some-- from that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I only remember that fellow I told you that was in Wüstegiersdorf.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I don't remember him from later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember him from Wüstegiersdorf.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't remember him from later on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You had-- you had hardly strength to talk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were dying next to you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, and the next day, you didn't see the people that you saw yesterday.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You don't know who is-- who was gone, who was--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
